quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  94,1,Have We not opened for you your head
  94,2,And lifted your burden off you
  94,3,"Which [burden] weighed upon your back"
  94,4,"And raised high the esteem, (in which) you (are held), for you"
  94,5,"With every difficulty then, indeed, there is a way out"
  94,6,"Indeed, with every difficulty there is a way out"
  94,7,"So then, when you get free (of your difficulty or from your worldly task), rise up"
  94,8,And turn to your Lord in complete devotion and submission